itunes:summary:
Ross Patterson and Dan Hollaway welcome special guest actor Tyler Grey from CBS’s “Seal Team” to discuss his experiences playing Trent on the show, Tyler gives some inside info on David Boreanaz’s life as an actor, shares stories from his previous movies “Suicide Squad” and “Snitch”, the 3 weigh in on their favorite war movies, and Tyler tells us why it would be his dream to work with Clint Eastwood.
